message.text:
Dreaming of taking your internship beyond borders? ✈️

Heads up, IABF Tamaraws, the world is waiting for you! ✨

Get ready to start your journey through the Work and Travel Program Orientation – your first step toward an exciting international experience! This orientation is designed for the new set of IABF interns eager to work abroad, gain global exposure, and represent the Tamaraw spirit across the world. 🔰

Don’t forget to scan the QR code or click the link within this post to register and secure your slot!

Link: https://forms.office.com/r/A56hHqSmdH

📍 September 22, 2025 | 1:30 PM | via MS Teams

Get ready to start your journey through the Work and Travel Program Orientation – your first step toward an exciting international experience! Don’t forget to scan the QR code or click the link within this post to register and secure your slot!

Link: https://forms.office.com/r/A56hHqSmdH

message.text:
Dreaming of taking your internship beyond borders? ✈️

Heads up, IABF Tamaraws, the world is waiting for you! ✨

Get ready to start your journey through the Work and Travel Program Orientation – your first step toward an exciting international experience! This orientation is designed for the new set of IABF interns eager to work abroad, gain global exposure, and represent the Tamaraw spirit across the world. 🔰

Don’t forget to scan the QR code or click the link within this post to register and secure your slot!

Link: https://forms.office.com/r/A56hHqSmdH

📍 September 22, 2025 | 1:30 PM | via MS Teams

message.text:
Dreaming of taking your internship beyond borders? ✈️

Heads up, IABF Tamaraws, the world is waiting for you! ✨

Get ready to start your journey through the Work and Travel Program Orientation – your first step toward an exciting international experience! This orientation is designed for the new set of IABF interns eager to work abroad, gain global exposure, and represent the Tamaraw spirit across the world. 🔰

Don’t forget to scan the QR code or click the link within this post to register and secure your slot!

Link: https://forms.office.com/r/A56hHqSmdH

📍 September 22, 2025 | 1:30 PM | via MS Teams
